{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act32side", "eventName": "水晶箭行動", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CR-3", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "假面舞池", "storyInfo": "虹彩小隊消除了與特克諾等人間的誤會，真正體會到了藝術家們新奇的想法和蓬勃的生命力。ELA將所見所聞告知了雷內爾，希望到街頭藝術社區落腳，雷內爾沒有拒絕。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g9_gangsters", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……呃，頭好痛。", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你醒了，大個子，來，這是冰塊，你的額頭腫了很大一個包。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你、你是攻擊我的那個小孩？", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再叫我一句小孩我就讓你後腦勺再腫一個包。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#3$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……發生什麼事？", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之就是，他們遺失的藥品找回來了，所以他們和我們之間的誤會也解除了……", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#2$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼藥品？什麼誤會？怎麼解決的？", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "透過一位可憐的司機先生，他的嘴很硬，但又沒那麼硬。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……我覺得更混亂了……我們現在在哪裡？", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，我扶你出去看看。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g8_slums", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的藥，請拿好。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦……謝謝……", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你叫什麼？在這裡打個勾。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#8$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克……好了。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，這裡還剩兩份。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我再從頭核對一下名單，說不定是有人忘了拿……看看還有誰沒來簽字。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……最後兩份藥是我的。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給你，特克諾小姐。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳……今天發生的事情我很抱歉，我們不知道搶劫事件另有他人指使……", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，這些藥品能物歸原主就是最好的結果。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#9$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古斯塔夫告訴我，這裡很多人都患有一種特殊疾病，如果沒有這些抑製藥劑，後果不堪設想。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話說，那個上尉不是之前和雷內爾不對盤嗎？為什麼一轉臉就要搶我們的藥來討好雷內爾？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米沃什告訴我，他是衝著雷內爾手裡對這片社區的開發權而來。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，有開發權又如何？這兩年就算雷內爾自己拿著開發文件不也一樣對我們束手無策。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那挺好，你們的社區文化很吸引人，就這樣被開發成酒店賭場我覺得很可惜。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不過是在這裡站了半天罷了，講得好像很瞭解這裡一樣。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過半天，但幾乎每個來領藥的人都極力向我推銷自己的藝術作品。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是要吃飯的嘛……話說你手臂上那是什麼？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是串刺繡手鍊，本來不打算買的，但是看見那孩子滿手都是針扎的痕跡……", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）誰家的孩子啊，這麼笨手笨腳的……", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛說什麼？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……我說……你想去我的工作室坐坐嗎？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g6_noblelivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_223"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "五千萬哥倫比亞金券，沒有再加價的嗎？", "name": "拍賣會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，五千萬金券落槌！", "name": "拍賣會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什麼……一直丟東西的倉庫？哪間倉庫？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#5$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是被你收購半年之後就倒閉的那家藥廠的倉庫。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，好像是有這麼回事……所以有人搶了那片社區的藥，栽贓到你們頭上，然後又想偷偷把藥運到那間倉庫去。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#6$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "準確來說，就是你頭上。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我現在該怎麼做？謝謝你幫我化解了這場誤會？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用謝，雷內爾先生。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽米沃什說你們打算離開我提供的住所了。怎麼，找到自己的朋友們了嗎？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我們只是找到了另外一處落腳的地方。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那片社區。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡？雖然我也沒什麼異議，但你們為什麼要離開？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#6$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在那裡看到了些很有意思的東西。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g9_gangsters", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡就是我的工作室了。這裡空間很大，我和其他的藝術家在這裡共同創作，尋找靈感，有的作品也在這裡展出。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些浸濕了的畫紙，看來是一些廢棄的靈感了？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，那個是作品。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作品？？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有個傢伙每畫完一幅畫都會把畫拿到室外，一直等到下雨，讓雨水化開已經鋪陳好的顏料，改變原有的畫面，這幅畫才算完成。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#10$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個正在展現自己完美肌肉線條的男人……應該在尋找靈感？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#10$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嚴格來說，他也是作品。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#2$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，行為藝術。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前面有個牌子，你要不要讀一讀？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“作品名，佩佩·圖里翁……作者，佩佩·圖里翁的父母……”", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“作品簡介，作者在作品問世半年後因嫌棄作品沒有經濟價值，將其丟棄至多索雷斯城郊……”", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“作者未曾想到……二十年後……佩佩·圖里翁……成為了多索雷斯的傳世名作……老傢伙們，後悔去吧！”", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇……", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#10$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，我是多索雷斯最偉大的源石技藝大師。你們是否想觀摩我的源石技藝？", "name": "嚴肅的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特克諾，他比你還厲害？", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在源石技藝上，無人能出其右。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗬。", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "展示的時候小心一點，可別傷到客人。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "嚴肅的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男人從口袋裡掏出數顆隱隱泛出橙黃色光芒的黑色晶體。四人謹慎地往後退了幾步。"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至純源石在男人寬大的掌心中滴溜溜旋轉，然後被男人挨個拋到天上——"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他開始用至純源石做拋接球。"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "數輪拋接之後，男人把所有的至純源石一口氣拋上天，仰面朝天，用鼻尖穩穩接住第一顆下落的至純源石。"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩顆，三顆，四顆……最終，所有的晶體一顆接一顆，在男人的鼻尖上穩穩疊成一座高塔。"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男人稍微側了側頭，至純源石疊成的塔幾乎平移一樣回到他的手心裡。"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "源石技藝……不是閃光、火球什麼的嗎？這……也是源石技藝？", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#10$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這難道不是源石？我剛剛展示的難道不是技藝？", "name": "嚴肅的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確……實……", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#10$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終於到了。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打開你們面前這扇門，就是我們最重磅的藝術品。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然這話最近好像說過，但我還想再說一次——我看見什麼都已經不會覺得奇怪了。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩個……大木偶的頭？這麼大？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這還只是頭呢，等身體組裝起來會更大。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的藝術節開幕那一夜，她們將成為兩位舞者。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當雙月緩緩落下，日光卻還沒照耀到我們的時候，她們將會起舞。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們會成為目光的焦點、藝術節的主角，她們會用最美的舞姿在街道上翩翩旋轉，她們會代替我們踩著韻律，轉遍整個社區。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很美的畫面。", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到那時，我想一定也會有許多人跟著人偶一起舞蹈吧。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，也許……", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我不知道。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道？", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#10$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……當年舞廳發生火災後，已經許久沒有人願意起舞了。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g6_noblelivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像我跟你說的，那裡有很多新奇的結構、充沛的情感、精妙的表達。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有意思……你的描述確實讓我對這些人在做的東西好奇起來了。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#6$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你打算去那個社區，不如替我去看看那裡的人究竟要做什麼。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是一直很反感他們把藝術節和你的開幕式定在同一天嗎？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不代表我不能對他們要做的東西感興趣。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以替你去看他們在做什麼，但我沒理由介入你和他們的衝突。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會讓你介入？當然，如果你真的能說動那些人，讓他們換個日子，我會非常感激。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這可沒辦法保證。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "試試總比不試好。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管怎麼說，你願意去瞭解那些人在做的事情讓我很驚訝。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#5$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你願意瞭解我，我想你應該就不會驚訝了。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為……", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "257號藏品音樂盒，一千五百萬金券起拍，有人要加價嗎？", "name": "拍賣會主持人"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓……現在我得專心投入進去了……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（舉牌）", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝您的競投，兩千萬，還有人要加嗎？", "name": "拍賣會主持人"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（舉牌）", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……同一人，加到二千五百萬？", "name": "拍賣會主持人"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（舉牌）", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你已經抬得夠高了，場子裡根本沒人跟你爭！", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（舉牌）", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我才不在乎別人出什麼價，我只想把它加到我心裡的價位。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，是我太魯莽了……", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我們確實也沒想到那群瘋子真有這麼無法無天，居然敢這麼羞辱聯合政府的職業軍人……", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白，明白！我下次——不，絕對沒有下次了！", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#6$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是再有下次，您撤了我的職，處分我，怎樣都可以！", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#6$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephone"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上尉……", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉嘴吧，這下上面也知道門口那個開卡車的活寶了。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他被脫光衣服扔到了我們辦公室大門口，上面覺得這是對聯合政府的公然侮辱。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們問我和雷內爾的合作關係還能不能維持，那塊地皮還有沒有希望拿到，我能說什麼？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*粗口*，這些個辦事不力的蠢貨。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上尉，我是想說，雷內爾的秘書來了……我們見還是不見？", "name": "帶隊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1271_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……讓他進來吧。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你是代表雷內爾來興師問罪的，那就免了吧。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#7$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會呢，馬特奧先生？雷內爾對您的效率是很滿意的，美中不足的是，您的行動方式多少有些冒險了。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那片社區的感染者數量不小，搶藥確實是個瓦解他們的方法。可您應該想到，假如真的有很多感染者因此去世……", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "處理不好，我們誰都無法交代。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這個問題我們已經意識到了。那他……還跟你說什麼了？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個嘛，他的意思是，既然之前太過冒險了，現在不如稍微謹慎一些，說不定還能有和平解決的餘地。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，都到這個時候了，你反而要我去跟那些人談判？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "馬特奧先生，您會錯意了，這事不用您操心，雷內爾先生已經派人去做了。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ELA小姐和她的小隊。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您想必很熟悉他們，我沒說錯吧？他們和您的手下打過照面，甚至還有人把您的手下和他們弄混呢。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不要忘了，米沃什，我們可是做了約定的。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#7$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "稍安勿躁，馬特奧先生，雷內爾不打算放棄和您合作，只是希望您能稍微冷靜一段時間。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地皮的事情，希望等您冷靜下來我們再談。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您還有什麼話要我帶給雷內爾先生嗎？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#10$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我先告辭了。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來……你*粗口*是耍著我玩來的，對吧，雷內爾？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#7$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*粗口*……雷內爾，要是我最後沒能從你手中拿到那塊地，你就死定了！", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#5$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g8_slums", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一億五千萬？他一個人把一個音樂盒加到一億五千萬？", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從他的出價來看，雖然這傢伙隨心所欲，但至少對他認定是藝術的東西還算真誠。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來你對他有些改觀……", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對他從來就沒有什麼意見，邁耶，他只是個很難捉摸的人。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是他有意思的地方？", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實……我承認，他不是傳統意義上那種無趣的藝術品商人。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能從你的口中聽到這樣的評價已經算是不錯了，很難得有一個你不那麼反感的雇主。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#8$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那之後呢？你打算繼續與他的契約嗎？", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#8$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不清楚……但我會考慮。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，我們是該謝謝他，如果不是他提供的幫助，我們不會這麼快適應這裡。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看在我們救了他的份上，不用客氣？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#10$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿……ELA，你能和我來一下嗎？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，什麼事？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是這樣的，老爹想要見你。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迪亞茲先生？他為什麼找我？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爹說有些問題想要當面問你。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我這就去見他。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有就是那個……期間他可能會表現得很兇……非常可怕。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦……他打算給我個下馬威。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然他自己不這麼認為，但……的確是的。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}